	<string>FitnessAI uses your location to show nearby events and gyms on the map.</string>
	<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
	<string>FitnessAI uses the camera for food barcode scanning, form video recording, and dual capture coaching videos.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>FitnessAI uses the microphone for voice memos and coaching video recordings.</string>
	<key>NSFaceIDUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Use Face ID for quick and secure sign in.</string>
	<key>NSHealthShareUsageDescription</key>
	<string>FitnessAI reads your steps, active calories, heart rate, and weight to display your daily health summary and auto-import weight check-ins.</string>
